Name: Math Fun
About the game: Math Fun is amazing fun loving app for everyone. This app will let you learn math in an fun and easy manner while playing. Features -High Quality Graphics in the App. -Play & Learn Addition, Subtraction, Division, Multiplication, Counting and Comparison. -In each Category there are 10 Levels. (Demo Version has 3 Levels). -Suitable for all age group. -Fully Tested on Windows 7 & above. -Ratings & Feedback Appreciated.
